Tom Virtue https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tom_Virtue 0 Thomas Edwin Virtue Jr. (born November 19, 1957), known as Tom Virtue, is an American actor. He is best known for his series regular role as Steve Stevens in the Disney Channel sitcom Even Stevens.
